      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个可观测性数据流的架构图，核心是用Alloy做数据收集和预处理，然后分发到Grafana后端。先从Auto-instrumenter开始吧，它负责自动埋点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Auto-instrumenter",
        "Alloy",
        "Grafana"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Auto-instrumenter是数据源头。它直接输出到Alloy的哪个组件？是通过OTLP协议吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Auto-instrumenter",
        "OTLP",
        "OpenTelemetry receiver"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，走OTLP协议，先到Alloy里的OpenTelemetry receiver。这个receiver专门接收遥测数据。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Auto-instrumenter",
        "OTLP",
        "OpenTelemetry receiver"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我画好了：Auto-instrumenter通过OTLP连到OpenTelemetry receiver。接下来receiver后面接什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Auto-instrumenter",
        "OTLP",
        "OpenTelemetry receiver"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "receiver后面要接一个Batch processor，做批量处理。而且这里要注意，metrics和traces是一起进去的，但后面要分开走。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "OpenTelemetry receiver",
        "Batch processor",
        "metrics",
        "traces"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
